article_title: Alaska Lawmakers Hire Star Lawyers To Block Obamacare Medicaid Expansion

article_metadata.description: Alaska legislators just hired Paul Clement, former Solicitor General under President George W. Bush, and one of his law partners Erin Murphy to sue Governor Bill Walker over his unilateral expansion of Medicaid under Obamacare.
article_metadata.author: The Apothecary
